mmetry was generated. If the charge asymmetry has ever existed and\nthe associated electromagnetic fields vanish in the asymptotic future, the\nlimit can be further reduced to $\\eta_Q<10^{-28}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Feb 2019 18:54:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Jun 2019 21:58:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 18 Nov 2019 04:53:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-19"}
