sult was proven\nfor the case $n=2$ by Rossman and Sultana. They called $m$ the number of bulges\nor the number of necks. We will slightly change the definition of $l$ to\ninclude immersed examples that contain the axis of rotation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Feb 2019 23:47:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Mar 2019 04:55:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 21 Mar 2019 01:20:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-22"}
