 new physics signals. The uncertainties quantified here are\nalso relevant for dark matter direct detection searches.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Feb 2019 04:25:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Feb 2019 17:46:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 21 Jun 2019 13:24:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-02"}
