\nPicnic, is secure in the quantum random-oracle model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Feb 2019 13:56:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2019 13:22:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 5 Mar 2020 09:10:01 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 27 Jul 2020 09:47:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-28"}
